definitions.definition: ( chiefly South Asia ) A marketplace or other open space in or by a city or town; an esplanade . [from 16th c.]

definitions.definition: Independence Square, the main city square in Kyiv, Ukraine.
The Orange Revolution protests that took place in Kiev’s Maidan in 2004–05; the Euromaidan protests of 2013–14; the protest movement associated with the 2014 Ukrainian Revolution .

main_definition: Independence Square, the main city square in Kyiv, Ukraine. [from 1993]
